{"tid":2351742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【So辱華】東京鐵塔點亮台灣國旗色","createTime":"2021-01-03T13:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T14:16:38.000Z","uid":2054,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"928204b7a9d45de7804cd3bf422dbb9faa480b11","tid":2351742,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"自由時報全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3400285\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3400285&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0Lnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=43d0ddaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3400285&h=553ccd4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3400285</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/03 20:37<br />\n〔駐日特派員林翠儀／東京3日報導〕「2021年新春台灣祭」今（3日）晚在東京鐵塔下的廣場點燈，除了各式台灣小吃美食之外，今年也請來東京媽祖廟的媽祖娘娘助陣，還有台南普濟殿的花燈將會場裝點得充滿台灣味，東京鐵塔還配合台灣祭，點亮象徵我國旗燈光，吸引日本民眾搶拍。<br />\n<br />\n今年受到疫情的影響，為避免人潮密集增加感染風險，主辦單位在加強防疫措施的情況下，還限制一次進場人數上限為600人，首日開幕人潮雖然明顯比往年減少，但有很多去年一整年無法訪台的日本民眾和台僑都到現場「充電」補充台灣能量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/01/03/3400285_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F3400285_1_1.jpg&h=c4458039&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06054962124f7eb5fb4ff314a97abae34c8ee447","tid":2351742,"uid":40415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"So"},{"pid":"c671a02773e8aee67e3876b79e118cae4e534324","tid":2351742,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06054962124f7eb5fb4ff314a97abae34c8ee447","tid":2351742,"uid":40415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"So"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face